+# Contributing
+
+## Dev environment
+- **VS Code Dev Containers** recommended. Open repo ‚Üí ‚ÄúRebuild and Reopen in Container‚Äù.
+- Or run locally via Docker: `docker compose up --build`
+- App ‚Üí http://localhost:3000
+
+## Common commands
+```bash
+pnpm dev          # run Next dev server
+pnpm build        # production build
+npx prisma studio # browse DB
+npx prisma generate && npx prisma migrate dev --name init
+pnpm run seed
+```
+
+## Branches & PRs
+- Branch from `main`: `feat/...`, `fix/...`, `chore/...`
+- Keep PRs small and focused; include **How to test** steps
+- CI must be ‚úÖ before merge
+
+## Code style
+- TypeScript strict by default
+- Keep components small; prefer server components unless you need client state
+- Avoid global side-effects; consider utility modules under `src/lib`
+
+## Database
+- Prisma schema lives in `prisma/schema.prisma`
+- Commit migrations (`prisma/migrations/**`)
+
+## Notes
+- Env vars: `.env.example` contains defaults; never commit real secrets
+- Node modules are ephemeral inside the Dev Container (tmpfs) and re-installed automatically
